## Architecture

User
  │
  ├── Web UI (Next.js)
  └── REST API client
        │
        ▼
[ FastAPI Backend ]
        │
        ├── POST /api/documents/upload
        │         │
        │         ▼
        │   [ File Type Detector ] ← python-magic
        │         │
        │         ▼
        │   [ Language Detector ] ← langdetect / lingua
        │         │
        │         ▼
        │   [ Format Router ] → correct ingester
        │         │
        │         ▼
        │   [ Plain Text ]
        │         │
        │         ▼
        │   [ Policy Composer ]
        │   Merges: active built-in rulesets +
        │           active custom rulesets +
        │           active custom recognizers
        │         │
        │         ▼
        │   [ Sanitizer ]
        │   Layer 1: Presidio (language-aware recognizers)
        │   Layer 2: HuggingFace NER (language-specific model, device-aware)
        │   Layer 3: Ollama (optional, context-aware)
        │         │
        │         ▼
        │   [ Anonymization Map (session-scoped) ]
        │   + Coreference Resolution
        │   + Unicode/locale normalization
        │         │
        │         ▼
        │   [ Semantic Chunker (format-aware) ]
        │         │
        │         ▼
        │   [ FAISS Embedder (multilingual MiniLM) ]
        │         │
        │   [ Persist: encrypted file + SQLite metadata ]
        │
        └── POST /api/chat/ask (SSE)
                  │
                  ▼
          [ Sanitize query (same pipeline) ]
                  │
                  ▼
          [ Retrieve top-k chunks (FAISS) ]
                  │
                  ▼
          [ Approval Gate ] → SSE → UI confirm/reject
                  │
                  ▼
          [ Cloud LLM ] ← masked text only
                  │
                  ▼
          [ De-anonymizer (local) ]
                  │
                  ▼
          [ SSE → UI: chat or JSON ]

